Fun place to visit. The art in the space is a bit sparse but I did enjoy the play on words for the title of the bar. They have many different beers on tap and bottled. The staff is very knowledgeable and will make suggestions based on what you like to drink. It can be intimidating because there is so much to choose from but the staff are very helpful. Also, it is very easy to walk right by this place. It is a few steps down off the sidewalk and there was some construction going on nearby. It's worth the discovery.
Great for a post work beer. Super cheap. Kinda grimey, if you're into that sort of vibe. Seemed like a hotspot for overworked, intelligent, bro-like grad students. Very loud.
